message.content:
Ka whakapau kaha ahau ki te āwhina i a koe. Whakapau kaha ki te whakamārama mai i ō whakapātari, ka whakautu ahau i ētahi pātai i roto i te reo Māori.

1. Te whakatakotoranga o tētahi pūkete hōputu:
   - Whakaritea i te rārangi o ngā tuhinga e hiahiatia ana ki roto i te pūkete.
   - Āwhina i te kaiwhakamahi ki te whakapau kaha i te pūkete, e whakarite ana i ngā whakaritenga tika.
   - Whakatakina te pūkete ki te rorohiko o te kaiwhakamahi, ā, whakamahi i te whārangi tukutuku e whakapau kaha ana i te whakapātari.

2. Te whakamahi i tētahi taupānga ā-ringa:
   - Te rapu i tētahi taupānga ā-ringa e hāngai ana ki tō whakapātari.
   - Tirotiro i te whārangi tukutuku o te taupānga, ā, whakaritea i ngā whakaritenga tika.
   - Tāpirihia ngā tuhinga e hiahiatia ana ki te taupānga, ā, whakapau kaha i te whakapātari.

3. Te whakaae i tētahi whakapātari tūpono:
   - Rapu i te whakapātari tūpono e hāngai ana ki tō whakapātari.
   - Whakaritea i ngā whakaritenga tika i roto i te whakapātari.
   - Whakatakotoria te whakapātari ki te rorohiko o te kaiwhakamahi, ā, whakapau kaha i
